    </article>

    <article class="knot-card">
      <h2>diagram data</h2>
      <dl class="knot-stats" id="knot-stats"></dl>
    </article>

    <article class="knot-card">
      <h2>crossings</h2>
      <div class="knot-output" id="knot-crossings"></div>
    </article>

    <article class="knot-card knot-wide">
      <h2>polynomial sketches</h2>
      <p class="knot-note">These are fast diagram invariants/readouts for exploration: writhe changes under R1; the bracket normalization is a compact crossing-sign summary, not a full knot table recognizer.</p>
      <div class="knot-output" id="knot-polys"></div>
    </article>
  </section>
</PageLayout>

<style>
